node.text:
Spent the week here in Minnesota building the track for round two of the championship. Amazing working with @andrewcarlson15 and crew. The track has so much elevation change, huge banks and zer-gravity drops. It’s windy and going to race really well. Almost no dust and great dirt here but we are intentionally not watering a few of the corners to see if the swept line could be a potential solution for other tracks where the soil blue grooves right away. Happy to get some laps on the CanAm to confirm the jumps are super smooth and will be easy on the cars.
@scott_speed @nitrocircus @yokohamatire @redbullmotorsports

node.text:
First test on the second of five @nitrorallycross tracks we are building this year was absolutely awesome! Take a ride with me for a lap at @erxmotorpark if you have a minute. Tickets on sale now (link in bio). Huge thanks to @andrewcarlson15 and the entire @carlsonmoto crew for the hospitality. And a few notes to any potential NRX competitors. the new @kmcwheels were magic.. We were able to run air pressure much lower and never had a single issue.
Whatever bead retention design that KMC have developed is making our lives easy. Also, we made the decision today after a lot of rain.. The @yokohamatire ‘s were designed for more traditional rx courses and I was unsure if we needed to allow the Yokohama Rally AO35 rally tire (which would have taken some work with current rim sizes) but the RallyCross AO54 became more fun to drive as the track conditions got muddier. Happy the weather didn’t cooperate because we were able to test and see that the tire exceeded our expectations. #perfecttestday #builtbydrivers #carsthatfly #tracksthatthrill @subarumotorsportsusa @nitrocircus @alpinestars @redbullmotorsports

node.text:
Spent the week here in Minnesota building the track for round two of the championship. Amazing working with @andrewcarlson15 and crew. The track has so much elevation change, huge banks and zer-gravity drops. It’s windy and going to race really well. Almost no dust and great dirt here but we are intentionally not watering a few of the corners to see if the swept line could be a potential solution for other tracks where the soil blue grooves right away. Happy to get some laps on the CanAm to confirm the jumps are super smooth and will be easy on the cars.
@scott_speed @nitrocircus @yokohamatire @redbullmotorsports

node.text: New @kmcwheels Awesome couple days on @burkemountainofficial putting the air slayers sti through its paces. Product testing and development is always a great chance for me to get seat time. Pavement hasn’t been my specialty on 2 or 4 wheels but I’ve enjoyed trying to figure it out. Big thanks to all the crew at @kmcwheels @yokohamatire and @subarumotorsportsusa for this opportunity. #scaryfast #fun #kmcwheels #kmcsubaru #kmcrally

node.text:
Found some footage of getting to ride Kenny Roberts JR’s Suzuki 500! Thanks for letting me borrow your helmet @sundersam !! What a week!
@subarumotorsportsusa @yokohamatire @nitrocircus @thehoonigans #thankyougoodwood @kmcwheels

The @fosgoodwood experience surpassed all of my expectations. From borrowing gear and riding Kenny Roberts JR’s moto gp bike up the hill at speed to sitting passenger with Jimmy McRae in one of Colin’s old Group A Subaru’s to flying a @takeongravity jet pack to racing @traxxas rc cars to a formal dinner in a castle with Duke Charles while we watched The Who play to 30 minutes of the best fireworks display I’ve ever witnessed.. and of course, racing the air slayer gymkhana wrx up the hillclimb! Also, stoked to finally meet the future female mx champion @oliviareynoldsmx and drift champion @jamesdeane130 .
@subarumotorsportsusa @yokohamatire @alpinestars @redbullmotorsports @kmcwheels @kuhl @motul

node.text:
Awesome day at the @fosgoodwood event. Qualified 1st in the hillclimb with my Subaru gymkhana car and got to drive one of Colin McRae’s old Subaru Group A legacys on the rally stage thanks to @dirtfishrally Steve Rimmer. Hopefully Sunday goes as well and we can get a win!
@yokohamatire @kmcwheels @subarumotorsportsusa @nitrocircus @redbullmotorsports @subarumotorsportsusa

node.text:
Fun day at @fosgoodwood .. got my first run up the hill. Big spectator turnout for a Thursday and some of the most insane cars I’ve ever seen in one place! Looking forward to the rest of the weekend.
@subarumotorsportsusa @yokohamatire @redbullmotorsports @kmcwheels @alpinestars
